      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ACES TO WIN (6) was a new acquisition for the Darryn Pateman stable last start when he made steady ground to run into third over 1500m at Albany. Can go a couple better. THE TOP BAR (3) finished fifth over 1435m at this track at his most recent appearance on August 12. Has found the right race. POWER TO RULE (7) took advantage of the good draw and raced on the pace last start before tiring to finish seventh over 1300m at Northam. Will give backers a sight. HOBELAR (4) returns from a spell of four-and-a-half months and is having his first run for a new yard. Finished sixth at Moora over 1000m when first-up last time in work. Fitter for a sixth in a recent trial over 930m at Lark Hill.",
